    "title": "Immediate Requirement Logistics Manager at Geodis India",
    "description": "Geodis India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Logistics Manager at our Delhi location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Geodis India:\nGeodis India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Geodis India!",
